# Phase 51.B — generated insight payloads are now durably mirrored in Postgres
# (engine.models.insight_payload); the on-disk JSON is a write-through cache and
# insight_detail falls back to the DB mirror when a file is absent. Stop tracking
# them so the repo + image stop carrying ~hundreds of generated files. Runbook:
# deploy the mirror code -> run scripts/backfill_insight_payload.py against prod
# -> `git rm -r --cached data/outputs` -> redeploy. See
# docs/INSIGHT_PAYLOAD_BACKFILL.md.
data/outputs/

